{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/2024-09-25-how-to-change-height-and-width-of-image-in-react-js/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aHoisting! To change height and width of image in react js, you can set  and  in . It will change height and width of image in react‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aHoisting!</p>\n<p>To change height and width of image in react js, you can set <code class=\"language-text\">width: 500px;</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">height: 400px;</code> in <code class=\"language-text\">.image-class</code>. It will change height and width of image in react js.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how to change height and width of image in react js.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import react component.</li>\n<li>Create a Component.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let‚Äôs start with the first step.</p>\n<h2>Step 1: Install and create a new React app.</h2>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Step 2: Import react component.</h2>\n<p>After installing, you have to import your React component.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> logo <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./zomato.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./App.css\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Step 3: Create a Component.</h2>\n<p>You can use <code class=\"language-text\">className=\"image-class\"</code> to change height and width of image in react js.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>img \n  src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>logo<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> \n  alt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Example\"</span> \n  className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"image-class\"</span> \n<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Change height and width of image example.</h2>\n<p>The below code is an example of a React. You have to import <code class=\"language-text\">'./App.css'</code> and set <code class=\"language-text\">width: 500px;</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">height: 400px;</code> in <code class=\"language-text\">.image-class</code> to change height and width of image in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> logo <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./zomato.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./App.css\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>img \n      src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>logo<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> \n      alt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Example\"</span> \n      className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"image-class\"</span> \n    <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.css</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.image-class</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 500px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 400px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">width: 500px;</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">height: 400px;</code> to change height and width of image in react js.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code.</p>\n